f the ride.\n\nFeatures:\n- First person realistic view\n- 7 tracks with beautiful views\n- 11 cars to use and customise\n- User friendly car control\n\n\nUpdate 1.01\n- Settings with on\\off music in game\n- New free ride drift mode\n- New huge mountain location for free ride\n\nChristmas update 1.02\n- New snowy track\n- New Christmas car\n- Added character with hands", "short_description": "Hey, do you need some drift?\nIf you are a fan of speed, and sharp turns, this game is for you. Pimp your skills of extreme driving and feel maximum control of your car. \n\nFeatures:\n- First person realistic view\n- 7 tracks with beautiful views\n- 11 cars to use and customise\n- User friendly car control\n\nChristmas update 1.02\n- New snowy track\n- New Christmas car\n- Added character with hands"}]}, "developer_name": "Raptor`s Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://raptorsreality.com/privacypolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://raptorsreality.com/privacypolicy.html", "publisher_name": "Raptor`s Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://raptorsreality.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "RACING", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "755537112722806"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974754_672022143545258_428979319184818176_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pzCe0XpqEhkQ7kNvgFDmJUK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scon